{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionclusterproperties"]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterProperties"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSDictionary"},{"type":"text","text":" object where the key is an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSString"},{"type":"text","text":". The dictionary key will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be the feature attribute key. The resulting attribute value is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"aggregated from the clustered points. The dictionary value is an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSArray"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"consisting of two "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSExpression"},{"type":"text","text":" objects."}],"metadata":{"title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterProperties","roleHeading":"Global Variable","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterProperties","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:@MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterProperties","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterProperties","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"var"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"extern"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:MLNShapeSource.h@T@MLNShapeSourceOption","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOption","text":"MLNShapeSourceOption"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"const"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionClusterProperties"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The first object determines how the attribute values are accumulated from the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"cluster points. It is an ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSExpression"},{"text":" with an expression function that accepts","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"two or more arguments, such as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"sum"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"max"},{"text":". The arguments should be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"featureAccumulated"},{"text":" and the previously defined feature attribute key. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"resulting value is assigned to the specified attribute key.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The second ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSExpression","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" in the array determines which","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"attribute values are accessed from individual features within a cluster.","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["let firstExpression = NSExpression(format: \"sum:({$featureAccumulated, sumValue})\")","let secondExpression = NSExpression(forKeyPath: \"magnitude\")","let clusterPropertiesDictionary = [\"sumValue\" : [firstExpression, secondExpression]]","","let options : [MLNShapeSourceOption : Any] = [.clustered : true,","                                           .clusterProperties: clusterPropertiesDictionary]"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This option corresponds to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"clusterProperties"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source property in the MapLibre Style Spec."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlin